data.description: This charming bungalow exudes originality and timeless appeal. Upon entering the front door, you are welcomed by a delightful enclosed porch, setting the tone for the inviting atmosphere within. The living room boasts a striking brick fireplace, complementing the adjacent formal dining area beautifully. With two bedrooms and one bathroom, this home offers comfortable living quarters. Noteworthy are the original hardwood floors that grace the entirety of the interior, adding to the home's character and allure. Outside, the backyard is enclosed by a privacy fence and features a covered patio. Schedule a showing today!
